com.storytron.swat

Class DummyEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.storytron.swat.DummyEngine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AbstractEngine

    public final class DummyEngine
extends java.lang.Object
implements AbstractEngine
    Empty implementation of the engine methods called by the interpreter. This implementation is used in the client for visiscript, where the engine is not present.
